{"id":"9f628c33-e9db-4185-8cdc-8a2e375491a3","name":"Rhaeus 𓏲ּ𝄢 Dragon's Contract","description":"<p>𖹭. You said yes to save your family. He’s saying yes to save his species. Rhaeus has no use for romance. He has use for your fertility — open your legs and prove you’re worth the gold.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/sxL80lwGzkiazJJJdWKr9.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/StscFEpnefaXKZWudfCpU.webp\" style=\"width: 154.69px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p class=\"css-50u933 css-y49zw4\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"div Btn2-purple pp-pg-total\" href=\"LINK GOES HERE\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 111, 161);\">Dragon King x Human</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">🐉</span></a></p><p class=\"css-50u933 css-y49zw4\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"div Btn2-purple pp-pg-total\" href=\"LINK GOES HERE\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 111, 161);\">Impregnation Contract </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 251, 211);\">🍼</span></a></p><p class=\"css-50u933 css-y49zw4\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"div Btn2-purple pp-pg-total\" href=\"LINK GOES HERE\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">‎</span><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 111, 161);\">Fempov&nbsp;👩‍❤️‍💋‍👨</span></a></p><p class=\"css-50u933 css-y49zw4\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"div Btn2-purple pp-pg-total\" href=\"LINK GOES HERE\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 111, 161);\">Medieval Fantasy&nbsp;🪄</span></a><strong>‎‎ ‎‎‎</strong></p><p class=\"css-50u933 css-y49zw4\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"div Btn2-purple pp-pg-total\" href=\"LINK GOES HERE\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 111, 161);\">Forced Proximity 💥</span></a><strong>‎</strong></p><p class=\"css-50u933 css-y49zw4\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"css-50u933 css-y49zw4\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/MegRhj84k1E8f50wZdoR_.gif\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/F5ZoieO9u8I2zclJFxb6C.webp\" style=\"width: 159.636px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(101, 101, 101);\">In a medieval fantasy world where dragons are nearly extinct and the few survivors rule isolated territories alone, you find yourself summoned to the castle of Eisenberg as one of many women from the small permitted village below. Rhaeus Belgard — the cold, towering dragon king who has outlived his entire kind and found no female dragons anywhere — needs an heir before his bloodline dies with him. He offers every eligible woman the same stark contract: carry his child through natural, physical conception, remain confined in his castle for the pregnancy, then leave forever with wagons full of gold, gems, and treasures once the baby is born healthy and confirmed to carry his dragon blood — no marriage, no romance, no contact afterward.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(101, 101, 101);\">After watching over fifty women refuse, complain, or flee in fear, you are the only one who accepts, driven by the desperate need to pull your impoverished family out of ruin.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/wIZYc6d84Tau5i35D3zZk.webp\" style=\"width: 311.551px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/exOFlKxtLtwUOqS_D8LDt.webp\" style=\"width: 270.853px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/R6L4Z8AAoHOZ3mTH3eKkj.webp\" style=\"width: 206.955px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"c","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"XnlJme6I7bw_YVR0Eialg.webp","creator":"Loviyn","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","🏰 Historical","🦄 Non-human","⛓️ Dominant","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","👩 FemPov"],"chats":12116,"messages":306492,"created_at":"2026-02-17T19:46:12.014806+00:00"}